# Plan Script Type: capture

# Plan Script Description:
# Remove network settings depending on the OS-Type before golden image capture. 
# Tested with RHEL 7.5, CentOS 7.5, SLE 15, XenServer 7.1, 7.6. Although Ubuntu 
# 19.04 does not generate fatal errors, it is not well integrated.

